表的代码预览提供

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('provide') and o.name = 'FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE_MEDICINE')
alter table provide
drop constraint FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE_MEDICINE
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('provide') and o.name = 'FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE2_FACTORY')
alter table provide
drop constraint FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE2_FACTORY
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('provide')
and name = 'provide_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index provide.provide_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('provide')
and name = 'provide2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index provide.provide2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('provide')
and type = 'U')
drop table provide
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: provide */
/*==============================================================*/
create table provide (
mno char(10) not null,
fno char(10) not null,
constraint PK_PROVIDE primary key nonclustered (mno, fno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: provide2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index provide2_FK on provide (
fno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: provide_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index provide_FK on provide (
mno ASC
)
go

alter table provide
add constraint FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE_MEDICINE foreign key (mno)
references medicine (mno)
go

alter table provide
add constraint FK_PROVIDE_PROVIDE2_FACTORY foreign key (fno)
references factory (fno)
go
